<subSubSection id="C34472A7FFFB6826459A3364BAB9F95F" pageId="14" pageNumber="297" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BE1212CFFFB6826459A3364BAB9F95F" blockId="14.[151,1437,1395,1746]" pageId="14" pageNumber="297">
<emphasis id="B92AFD3EFFFB6826459A3364BB40F904" bold="true" box="[199,315,1647,1673]" pageId="14" pageNumber="297">Remarks.</emphasis>
Previously 
<taxonomicName id="4C5E5AAFFFFB68264499337BB8ECF904" authorityName="Cartwright" authorityYear="1990" box="[452,663,1648,1673]" class="Insecta" family="Ecnomidae" genus="Ecnomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="297" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="woronan">
<emphasis id="B92AFD3EFFFB68264499337BB8ECF904" box="[452,663,1648,1673]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="297">Ecnomus woronan</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was recorded from many localities in the NT and northern WA and only one site in northern 
<collectingRegion id="499AEFCEFFFB682644E63398B844F920" box="[443,575,1683,1709]" country="Australia" name="Queensland" pageId="14" pageNumber="297">Queensland</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFCF5CDDFFFB6826470D3398B96BF920" author="Cartwright, D. I." box="[592,784,1683,1709]" pageId="14" pageNumber="297" pagination="1 - 48" refId="ref14543" refString="Cartwright, D. I. (1990) The Australian species of Ecnomus McLachlan (Trichoptera: Ecnomidae). Memoirs of the Museum of Victoria, 51, 1 - 48. https: // doi. org / 10.24199 / j / mmv. 1990.51.01" type="journal article" year="1990">Cartwright 1990</bibRefCitation>
). The species is recorded from a further nine sites in the NT.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
